We can download and store variants of BERT in this directory. The downloaded model can be called directly in embeddings.py
(I have not uploaded the model here due to its large size)

Currently used model is: 'bert-base-nli-mean-tokens'

Link to download variants of BERT model: 
https://public.ukp.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de/reimers/sentence-transformers/v0.2/ 
